Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:00:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what... does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only work for one week!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY groans]\NDon't you mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] You could've eaten it if\Nyou had just taken the bug out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It took three full\Ndays of hard cooking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to prepare that soup for\Nyou, and you wasted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the customer here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand me?!\NI'm paying you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...truly satisfy your hunger?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NI'm asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it satisfy your hunger?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "Unwelcome Customer!\NSanji's Food and Ghin's Debt!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[toilet flushes]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN A]\NJust hold it... almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NCustomer service equals love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And love equals restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NThe customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...is the king! [screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleasant greetings to the\Ncustomer is what it's all about,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the customer is always right,\Nand we stand by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello and welcome,\Nyou damn crooks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you ever come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Awfully sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all so pathetic, I laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NDone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PATTY] Ah! Yes, indeed!\N--[MAN A gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Today will be a great\Nday for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello there and\Nwelcome, you damn crook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our service\Nmotto around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,no doubt about it, the\Ncustomer is-- Ah! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NOh, no! Our customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Not again, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're\Ndoing to our customer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see he's\Na Marine Lieutenant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a terrible cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that\Nyou can talk to me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:04:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY grunts] A crappy cook\Nlike you is calling me bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Restaurants can't exist\Nwithout their customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're our lifeblood, so\Nwe don't want to hurt them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you seem to keep doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But he deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't treat the food\Nor me with respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he insulted\Nall the cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--[FULLBODY grunts]\N--[SANJI] So I simply
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,taught him a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY grunts]\NYou're gonna to regret this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No restaurant should treat\Nits customers like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shut you down...\NDo you understand me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will shut you down!\NThis entire place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole restaurant is\Nfinished! Do you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, maybe I should\Njust finish you off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK LI]\NSous Chef Sanji, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COOK LI yelling]\N--Arrogant assholes like you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,who think they're such big shots\Nthey can push anybody around
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,really piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep doing this in\Nthe restaurant every other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not such a big\Nshot now, are ya? Are ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF, LUFFY grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--[CUSTOMER A] What happened?\N--[CUSTOMER B] Are they okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]\NI can breathe again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Zeff,\Nwhat's happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't hurt\Nyourself, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing that's gonna have\Nto get fixed because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all your\Nfault, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it my fault?!\NYou attacked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, can you stop messing\Naround and give us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji's gone crazy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS, SANJI growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZEFF] Hey, Sanji!\N--[SANJI growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NDon't tell me you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,went on another rampage\Nin here, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a cork in it, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Oh, now you're\Nordering me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who do you think\Nyou're talking to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to\Nsink my restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the bottom of the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--[FULLBODY laughs]\N--[ZEFF] You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your ass out\Nof my restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY groans, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY] What kind\Nof restaurant is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That boss is like a gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if... if...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...this were a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you deny our motto\Nthat the customer is king?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The only kingly customers are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the ones who stomach the\Nslop that you call food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.\NIf you two wanna fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll keep it in the\Nkitchen, you understand me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY grunts] Are all\Nthese idiots really cooks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE B]\NLieu-Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Fullbody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE B panting]\NWe've... We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this restaurant is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, he's escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Krieg's henchman\Nattacked us and vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sir, we've already\Nlost seven of our men,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only thing we wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,out of him was a lead\Non finding Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When we picked him\Nup three days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,he was right on the verge\Nof starving to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And we haven't fed him anything.\NWhere'd he get the strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Krieg Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER D] They're the one's\Nwho're said to be the fiercest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,pirates in the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Lieutenant, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem we have\Na new customer, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd do well to mind his manners
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and not start any\Ntrouble on my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A pirate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what it is...\NJust bring me something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... This is a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello and welcome,\Nyou damn crook!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna say\Nthis one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me something to\Neat and make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That cook is gonna\Nget us killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, right away,\Nbut might I be so bold
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to inquire how you're\Npaying for your meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will a bullet be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have\Nany money then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,--[FULLBODY] What?\N--[CUSTOMERS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That dumb ass, Patty,\Nbroke another chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... What power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, pirate, but our policy is\Nto only serve paying customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--[CUSTOMERS whistle, cheer]\N--You tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick his ass, Patty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Show that pirate we\Ncooks don't screw around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[stomach rumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NAww, I can hear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,your stomach grumbling\Nfrom here, pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a fart, jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me... something...\Nto eat now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not getting you\Nanything, so beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY]\NI can't take anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these cooks are insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything to do\Nwith this place ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[cheering continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NAnd now, you damn crooks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need anything,\Njust ask, okay? [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And please, never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN groans]\NDammit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,if I wasn't so weak from hunger,\NI'd be inside eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] And he'd be lying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not hungry,\Nby any chance, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] No... I'm not...\NJust leave me alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[stomach rumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--[door creaks]\N--[LUFFY] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NTake it and leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept charity;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter how\Ndown and out I may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take this stuff away, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your whining\Nand eat it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what\Nthey say in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, if anyone's hungry,\Nthey're a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm\Nnot your customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[stomach rumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] It's amazing\Nhow beautiful and cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,this ocean can be, how it's\Nalmost a death sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to lose your food\Nand water out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how difficult it is to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it\Nmeans to go hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the sea\Nmore than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can die for your\Npride if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But listen, if you\Nand eat and survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,won't that give\Nyou the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to fight for pride\Ntruly worth having,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,now and in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN sobbing]\NI'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...\NThank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was over, I truly\Nthought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN sobbing]\NThis food...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never eaten food\Nthis good before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN sniffling, snorting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just found my cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky he\Ngave you some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't lookin' so\Ngood there... [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So listen, Mr. Cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you leave this\Nboat and join my crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use a cook like\Nyou on my pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI, GHIN]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NSo you're a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you went and\Ndid a crazy thing like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,shoot a cannonball\Ninto the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was self-defense that\Nturned into a stray shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NA stray shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you\Nreally don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,do anything stupid\Nto this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner used to be a cook\Nin a famous pirate fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh... So the old man...\Nused to be a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This restaurant is everything\Nto that crazy old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only treasure he'll\Nneed for the rest of his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll do anything to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of which,\Nall of the cooks who
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,joined him out of\Nrespect and admiration
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,are just as hot-headed\Nas any pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Which helps since\Npirates are always
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,coming and going\Nout of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah, I've noticed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really wild\Nrestaurant, huh? [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So true... And this is\Nhow it is every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten so bad that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,customers are coming\Nhere just watch fights
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,between the cooks\Nand the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, it's been a new\Npirate ship and a new rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't long till all the\Nwaiters got scared and bailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why the old man wanted\Nme to work for him for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you joining my\Npirate crew or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a reason I have to\Nwork here in the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I can't just\Nwalk away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't accept?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to accept your refusal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good cook,\Nand I need one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's obvious that we\Nshould be pirates together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]\NListen to what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave here, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your reason for staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to\Ntell you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you just said\Nto listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you my answer was no,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's all you\Nneed to hear from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now take you pirate ship, and\Nfind a cook someplace else
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,before I cut you up, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You listen to me, jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No one makes fun of my straw hat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,unless they're\Nready for a beating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NI'm sorry to interrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, SANJI]\NWhat is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ghin,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm a crew member of\NDon Kreig's Pirate fleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say that you're\Na pirate yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And pretty soon, I'm gonna sail\Nthe Grand Line and find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't have been\Nseeking it for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't even\Nhave a cook yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,your crew can't be all that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, he's only\Nthe fifth member.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'm not going,\Nso don't count me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like a nice kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so let me give you some\Nfriendly advice, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line is a\Nplace you want to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still young, there's\Nno need to rush into anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, the Grand Line is one\Nsmall part of this entire ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be a real\Npirate, there are plenty of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,other places out here\Non the seas to explore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHmm... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you just\Ntell me what to avoid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Grand Line now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is why I fear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] For being a\Ncrewmember of Don Kreig's,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a pretty\Nwimpy pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm? Who's Don Kreig?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK B] The appetizer\Nfor table three is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D] Yeah, well you're gonna\Nhave to take it out yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the last waiter's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You think more of them\Nwill be comin', Patty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the guy\Nyou beat up earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in the restaurant was\None of Don Krieg's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that will make\Nthe rest of them very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh... I don't care\Nwhose man he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All I'm saying is, the stories\NI've heard say Don Krieg is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the strongest,\Nfiercest and most evil
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,pirate in this\Npart of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NOn these waters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,his grip of fear\Nreaches far and wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He commands over\N50 pirate captains,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the largest\Npirate fleets ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He is truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that his\Nextraordinary fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of ships has more than\Nfive thousand pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be bad\Nfor Boss Zeff...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If that guy you beat up\Ngoes to Don Krieg and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,tells him what you did,\Nand he sends just one ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be enough\Nof us to fight them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be crushed, like\Na grape under an elephant,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and left to sink to the\Nbottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying I should\Nhave just served him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so he could experience our
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,great customer service\Nand meals for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think that\Nwould have been rude
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to the other damn\Ncrooks who pay money?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never stoop that low!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Baratie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The fighting cooks have a\Nreputation to uphold, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never ruin that. I don't\Ncare who that pirate cries to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them send their ships.\NI'll fight them all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're scared, quit and\Nlet the real cooks work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare say that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of all that\Nbig talk you spit out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which is why all the\Nwaiters jumped ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that's happening\Nnow is all your fault, Patty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Those waiters\Nwere worthless wimps
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment a customer\Nshowed up! Worthless wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COOKS cheering]\N--[COOK B] Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COOKS cheering]\N--[COOK A] Take him out, Carne!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D] He doesn't\Nstand a chance, Patty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, what's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NYes, Boss Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So long, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the warning,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm still gonna\Ngo to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a stranger,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't stop you from\Ngoing anywhere you wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to give\Nyou a fair warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And to you, Chef...\NThank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my life,\Nand I owe you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cooking skills are\Nthe best I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to come\Nback again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a seat for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore Boy, get up\Nhere right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBoss Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ghin... Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll probably get\Nyelled at or fired
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause you gave me\Nthat food for free...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWhatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there's not proof,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's no way for\Nme to get yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps, sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Try not to get\Ncaught again, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NThank you again, Chef Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forget\Nyour kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NSanji! Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK E]\NHey, table three is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm gonna be the new\Nchore boy around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of us was\Nsupposed to make that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to\Nmake that, I'm too busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too busy being a jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again, I dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS] Don't just sit\Nthere picking your nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go wash the dishes or\Nsomething... Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NHas anyone seen Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK I] I think I saw\Nhim hittin' on a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Boss Zeff\Nwould get rid of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad enough\Nhe's the Sous Chef,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's never in the\Nkitchen doing his job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK J]\NI think we're stuck with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's worked here\Nlonger than any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK J]\NHe was working the kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the dining room\Neven before I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK L] Yeah, but even so,\NI just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,--[dish shatters]\N--Why does he stay here when
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he and Boss Zeff\Nare always fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK J] I think he's\Nwants to be the Head Chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK O]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PATTY] Hmm?\N--[dish shatters]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how many of these dishes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,have you gone and\Nbroken into tiny pieces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] You know what?\N--[dish shatters]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to count! Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY] I wasn't being\Nserious, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you breaking them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK P] Stop screwing around,\Nand clean up your mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat, I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't take the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK J]\NThat was a perfect entree!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NYep! Pretty tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOw ow ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NGet out of our kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we have you take\Norders in the dining room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ask the customers\Nwhat they want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that simple enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These chores sure are boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if Coby got tired\Nof all this work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard you had to work\Nhere for a whole year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if we redraw\Nthe flag for our ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps] You're eating all\Nthis delicious food without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of crew are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on... I think that's our\Nbusiness, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NTake this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy... This is\Ngonna be so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP, NAMI snickering]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I have to say the food\Nhere is really quite delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI snickering]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be\Ndrinking this yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY choking]\N--[USOPP, NAMI laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI can't believe you did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I can't\Nbelieve you did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screaming]\NAw, that was nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--[CUSTOMERS murmuring]\N--[LUFFY coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--[CUSTOMER F growling]\N--Aren't they... quaint...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's\Nthe rest of his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY screaming]\N--[GROUP laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish pouring it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear ocean, thank\Nyou for this treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you have shared\Nfrom your depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear this hardship\Nof loving you from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It is too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now prepared to sail to the\Nends of the earth as a pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if it means someone of your\Nrare beauty will be by my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZORO growling]\N--[LUFFY chuckles nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To be together sailing the seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But how tragic a great\Nobstacle blocks our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] And that great\Nobstacle would be me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI sighs]\NStupid geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an opportunity you\Ndon't want to pass up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not join them\Nand become a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need to keep\Nyou here at my restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[squawking]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NI see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This cook saved your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were able\Nto return here to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you\Nare saying... Ghin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.87,0:22:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NY-Yes... but you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea the main ship was\Nin this condition, Don Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NSo, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I believe I'll take you\Nto the Sea Restaurant Baratie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.11,0:23:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:23:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.86,0:24:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.86,0:24:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.12,0:24:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NCustomer is king!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.84,0:24:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] That's right! Give a\Nsmile no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.38,0:24:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHey, there's a big fish here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.05,0:24:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThat's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.64,0:24:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NKrieg's Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.97,0:24:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] They're a huge\Nfleet with five thousand men!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.64,0:24:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NFive thousand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.98,0:24:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope we have enough chairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.19,0:24:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NYou idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.94,0:24:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to attack this\Nplace! Close the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.27,0:24:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.98,0:24:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Strongest Pirate Fleet!\NCommodore Don Krieg!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

